post_text: Happy Labor Day!
text: Happy Labor Day!

post_text:
Have you filled out your 2020 Census yet? 10 minutes will help ensure our community receives enough resources for 10 years. The Census provides funding for schools, hospitals, after-school programs and more! To fill out the census please visit my2020census.gov or call 844-330-2020 A special thanks to Grasiela Rodriguez for creating this amazing mural at Potrero School!
#CaStudentsCount #LACcensuschalkathon #WeCountLA

post_text:
Dear El Monte City School District, Parents, Students, and Staff,

We are very excited to welcome you to the 2020-21 school year! The first day of school is August 20th. Even though we are starting in distance learning, we can't wait to "see" you!

This year, to celebrate the first day of school, we are encouraging you to post first day of school pictures and use our hashtag #EMCSDFirstDay on social media. We invite you to help us spread cheer for the start of our new school year!

You can post photos directly to our EMCSD accounts: Facebook @ElMonteCSD and Instagram @ElMonteCitySD. Since we are unable to access photos you post on your personal Facebook or Instagram pages, make sure you share them with us. You can also email your photos to pics@emcsd.org, and we will happily add them to our Back to School album.

Be sure to share your captured memories with us!
